text: Odontosagda superbum is a species of air-breathing land snail, a terrestrial pulmonate gastropod mollusk in the family Sagdidae. == Distribution == This species occurs in Departement de l'Ouest in Haiti.invertebratezoology, The UF Invertebrate collection, "Odontosagda superbum FLMNH, Invertebrate Zoology, 171140-Mollusca", iDigBio, Published January 25, 1978.
